Comment: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:26.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,next episode title: Night Talk

Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:14.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:27.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I cleaned it, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:31.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:35.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:42.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit crying; it's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:48.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan, what happened with Kazehaya earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell him that you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:03.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're not going out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows! Who knows what could have happened in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have said “yes” in the heat of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:24.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan, do you think it's possible for Kazehaya-kun to fall for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:30.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even have anyone to talk to until just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:35.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya doesn't care about that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice, and he's caring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:51.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he makes his own judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he smiles, you feel relieved and smile back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:59.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he gets angry when he needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:00.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sort of short-tempered, and he hates anything that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's popular with both the guys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cute—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:18.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've talked to anyone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:24.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan accepts me for who I am, even after everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan is like Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:39.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in high school, and everyone's cheering me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have made him notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun thinks I like Arai Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:59.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I say, he's only going to think I'm saying it because I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:16.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always known that Kazehaya doesn't think anything special of me.{T: otherwise people might think she's talking about Pin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:22.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore, whether he finds out or gets the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:33.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want Kazehaya-kun to think I like Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:37.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a misunderstanding. He'll understand if you tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:43.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he'll understand if I tell him the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:46.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.{T: can't argue with that}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:56.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I still wouldn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:01.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We both like Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:04.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We both feel the same way about the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:11.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet we can't be friends, even though we have the same feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:17.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what will that make us, Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we be nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:26.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will we be something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your stomach okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me, disappearing all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at the game tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.41,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:56.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan, let's be in the same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm friends with Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same group, yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyagawa said he likes Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miki has always liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:35.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi lent Miyagawa her notes and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:39.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't like it when a guy likes any girl besides herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she acts as if she likes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bitch.{T: QFT}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:46.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi my ass, her name's Ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:49.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We let her in our group so we could talk to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:53.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get in her way if she ever starts to like someone.{@ha, told you someone's screwing with her cuz they're jealous}{T: you win}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got in our way already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:03.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been a little bummed lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.{for tgen:p}{T: AE HAET U}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do club work in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to skip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have club work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just came to pick something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:16.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees me for who I am.{T: an evil scheming bitch? nay.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:45.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Kazehaya likes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:12.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't care if Kazehaya finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you liked Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:40.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bitch, acting all nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Sawako-chan like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's easily misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she always speaks the truth, even when it's risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:05.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when Kuronuma says something, I believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she agrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:17.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if she always played it safe, Yoshida and Yano might not have trusted her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:23.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as you want to help her, she always does it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:27.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she really worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:34.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a misunderstanding. He'll understand if you tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sound so stuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kazehaya got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:12.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.19,0:11:23.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:36.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't think I like someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:07.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make myself think of anyone else more than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:09.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:23.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at least a little happy that I confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.{@they're both anorexic}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:44.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me by my first name, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this old-ass name isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I wasn't going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally screwed up my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calculations?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:10.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you that made me screw up the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're never going to meet anyone as cute as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why would I like that dumbass Pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:34.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a good eye for women, do you?{@pwned}{T: truth!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:58.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we might have understood each other better if Kurumi-chan and I had liked two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:16.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what made you realize you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:30.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she had liked someone else, I might not have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:37.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how aggressive she is when it comes to guys. I admire her in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:51.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's good news, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going to get a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:02.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:08.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could tell Kurumi-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:16.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was glad when she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with those shades?{@and this is how lady gaga came to be}{T: I thought that was some dude getting a sex change}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, what's up with those sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunglasses are for outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:45.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that kid that likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you cry yourself out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like someone your own age next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:16:05.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With high school kids, you tell them that you like them, and they'll be thinking about you all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win the rest of the soccer games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:31.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win and party like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy when I fell for him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything when people said nice things about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never told anyone how much I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always kept it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:09.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any crazy fluke things work out between you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate any woman that Kazehaya likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be friends, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:50.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I was pissed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:02.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have liked her if she'd always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:14.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost every game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My steak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai-sensei lost his spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sports day ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:27.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head home and party at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:35.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Party? My first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:41.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I went home and looked it up in the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My first rival.{@ok she's asperger's}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, since when have you liked him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about since his public confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Public confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I doubt it, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:15.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I had feelings for him by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:25.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I started feeling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:37.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, what are you singing next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:42.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she went outside because her face got red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:53.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, who made her get red?{@is the baseball guy drunk?}{T: too many lemonade! It's not for girls...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sleep-talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:41.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I over thought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:57.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My world had changed that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:11.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd fallen in love the moment he called my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:34.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Night Talk
